data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and well-designed newer construction home in The Village at Towne Lake. This Frisco floorplan offers a modern and stylish living space with a thoughtful layout, catering to both entertaining and relaxation. The attention to detail in features like the open-concept kitchen/dining/family room, the owner's suite with a custom walk-in closet and spa-like ensuite bathroom, and the covered deck for morning coffee provides a high level of comfort and luxury. This professionally-designed home has hardwoods in all living areas and tile in all baths and laundry room. The 11' ceilings on the main level, 10' ceilings on the second level, and 8' interior doors throughout contribute to a spacious and elegant atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen with 42" cabinets, Quartz countertops, and stainless appliances, along with the linear fireplace in the family room create an inviting space for gathering. The Frisco floorplan offers a modern and stylish living space with a thoughtful layout, catering to both entertaining and relaxation. The Village at Towne Lake is a beautifully maintained and gated enclave of courtyard-style homes close to downtown Woodstock. The community offers a range of excellent amenities, including a pool, pickleball court, bocce ball, fire pit, dog park, clubhouse, fitness center, and more. This is the perfect opportunity to get all the benefits of a new construction home at a price that can't be beat! $1500 lender credit with our preferred lender!
